### Hadith 2:135

*Narrated Abbas bin Tamim*

that his uncle (who was one of the companions of the Prophet) had told
him, "The Prophet went out with the people to invoke Allah for rain for
them. He stood up and invoked Allah for rain, then faced the Qibla and
turned his cloak (inside out) and it rained."

